2026-03-05 15:14:50 - StudioAtrium\Entity\Discuss\Post:Insert {"timestamp":1772723690,"user_id":19355,"user_ip":"46.112.67.117","user_browser":"Mozilla\/5.0 (iPhone; CPU iPhone OS 26_2_1 like Mac OS X) AppleWebKit\/605.1.15 (KHTML, like Gecko) CriOS\/145.0.7632.108 Mobile\/15E148 Safari\/604.1","dao_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\Discuss\\Post\\DAO\\PDOMySQL","dao_event":"dao_object_insert","entity_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\Discuss\\Post","entity_data":{"id":11538,"__foreign_props":[],"parent_id":"0","cat_id":"4","author_id":19355,"project_id":"1744","nick":"\u0141ukasz","topic":"\u015arodek, koszty budowy projektu","content":"Dzie\u0144 dobry, jeste\u015bmy bardzo powa\u017cnie zainteresowani projektem, bardzo bym prosi\u0142 o jakie\u015b zdj\u0119cia \u015brodka domu, lub lokalizacj\u0119, \u017ceby w razie czego mo\u017cna by\u0142o si\u0119 um\u00f3wi\u0107 i ogl\u0105dn\u0105\u0107 dom. \r\nJestem z wojew\u00f3dztwa ma\u0142opolskiego. \r\nTe\u017c interesuje mnie ile wyni\u00f3s\u0142 koszt budowy tego domu do stanu deweloperskiego.\r\nW razie ch\u0119ci kontaktu prosz\u0119 o wiadomo\u015b\u0107 lub zdj\u0119cia  na adres mailowy lukasz.pacyga90@gmail.com\r\nZ g\u00f3ry dzi\u0119kuj\u0119, pozdrawiam","create_date":"2026-03-05 15:14:50","modify_date":"2026-03-05 15:14:50","status":"published","is_moderated":0,"attachments":[],"_uid":2953775},"entity_changes":false}
