2026-03-11 06:59:23 - StudioAtrium\Entity\User\Message:Update {"timestamp":1773212363,"user_id":19170,"user_ip":"5.173.198.86","user_browser":"Mozilla\/5.0 (Linux; Android 10; K) AppleWebKit\/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome\/145.0.0.0 Mobile Safari\/537.36","dao_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\User\\Message\\DAO\\PDOMySQL","dao_event":"dao_object_update","entity_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\User\\Message","entity_data":{"id":1490,"__foreign_props":[],"user_id":"19170","parent_id":"1489","author":"Studio Atrium","title":"Re: Wektor Xv","message":"<p>Dzie\u0144 dobry Pani Gabrielo<\/p>\r\n<p>Mo\u017ce Pani skorzysta\u0107 z <a href=\"https:\/\/www.studioatrium.pl\/parter\/Wektor-xv,1718.html\">funkcjonalno\u015bci<\/a> na naszej stronie, kt\u00f3ra umo\u017cliwia zmierzenie sobie pomieszcze\u0144.<br \/>W za\u0142\u0105czniku znajdzie Pani pogl\u0105dowe materia\u0142y do bardzo podobnego projektu, o takich samych gabarytach bry\u0142y i bardzo zbli\u017conej funkcjonalno\u015bci oraz wielko\u015bci pomieszcze\u0144 - projekt <a href=\"https:\/\/www.studioatrium.pl\/projekty-domow\/Wektor-xii,1659,lustro.html\">Wektor XII<\/a>.<\/p>\r\n<p>Dokumentacj\u0119 projektow\u0105 rozpoczniemy tworzy\u0107 w momencie z\u0142o\u017cenia zam\u00f3wienia na ten projekt.<\/p>\r\n<p>W przypadku dodatkowych pyta\u0144, pozostaj\u0119 w kontakcie.<\/p>\r\n<p>Pozdrawiam<br \/>\u0141ukasz Jakubiec<\/p>","create_date":"2026-03-09 13:26:13","status":"read","attachments":{"UserMessageFile":[{"id":52312,"__foreign_props":[],"profile_name":"UserMessageFile","filename":"69aebc78a101f-gl_1585-wt21-pb21-wektor_xii-rzuty-przekroje.pdf","path":"36\/381476","title":"Wektor XII - rzuty i przekroje","description":"","owner_uid":"381476","props":{"original_filename":"GL 1585-WT21-PB21-Wektor XII-rzuty-przekroje.pdf","file_size":931231,"file_created":1773059192},"sorting":0,"parent_attachment_id":0,"parent_relationship":"","_uid":13391877,"childAttachments":[]}]},"_uid":381476},"entity_chang